0.1.name: wordpress/duckduckgo-search
0.1.description:
DuckDuckGo is a search engine that emphasises privacy and search quality. This plugin adds a search widget to your site that lets users search the site using DuckDuckGo.

If you come across any bugs or have suggestions, please use the plugin support forum or email me. I can't fix it if I don't know it's broken!

Note: this plugin is not maintained by the DuckDuckGo team; issues should be reported to the plugin author and not to DuckDuckGo support.
